g","name":"Open","id":"1","statusCategory":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/statuscategory/2","id":2,"key":"new","colorName":"blue-gray","name":"To Do"}},"components":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/10203","id":"10203","name":"Installation Guide"}],"timeoriginalestimate":null,"customfield_13000":null,"description":"Vic provided an outline for a better, fail-fast (rather than slow and painful) installation process\r\n-search “install eucalyptus” results should land on a process/outline, not installing a package\r\n-Install services one after the other (each completely, rather than bouncing around, machine to machine, as it is now)\r\n-Prereqs in each section\r\n-Verify in each section\r\n-Combined verification after install and networking complete\r\n","customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":null,"customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"attachment":[],"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"summary":"Install Guide needs reorganization","creator":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=kmeredith","name":"kmeredith","key":"kmeredith","accountId":"557058:ad01e29f-e62e-4f95-b458-a96ea25c65e5","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Keri Meredith","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"subtasks":[],"reporter":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=kmeredith","name":"kmeredith","key":"kmeredith","accountId":"557058:ad01e29f-e62e-4f95-b458-a96ea25c65e5","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Keri Meredith","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"customfield_10000":null,"aggregateprogress":{"progress":0,"total":0},"customfield_12100":"0|i03adj:","customfield_10001":null,"customfield_10200":null,"customfield_10002":null,"customfield_10003":null,"customfield_10400":null,"customfield_12500":null,"customfield_10116":null,"customfield_11600":["kmeredith(kmeredith)"],"customfield_10117":null,"environment":null,"customfield_11800":null,"customfield_11802":null,"customfield_11805":null,"duedate":null,"customfield_11806":null,"progress":{"progress":0,"total":0},"votes":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/DOC-1615/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"comment":{"comments":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/37059/comment/89447","id":"89447","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=kmeredith","name":"kmeredith","key":"kmeredith","accountId":"557058:ad01e29f-e62e-4f95-b458-a96ea25c65e5","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Keri Meredith","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Notes from 6/19/2015 meeting with Vic & Garrett ([~viglesias] and [~gholms], correct any errors or omissions please!)\r\n\r\nAs per the bug description (above) the idea is to _fail fast_ and, when the customer searches, they find the *high-level PROCESS* (see below) and not the 4th step into the install (as it is today). Today's QA Chef recipes are geared toward fail-fast, and builds up as it goes. \r\nhttps://github.com/eucalyptus/eucalyptus-cookbook/tree/master/recipes\r\n\r\nHigh-level Install Guide organization should be something like this:\r\nA. Install (see below for details on this)\r\nB. Network (stuff Scott's working on)\r\nC. Verify (once install and network done, how to ensure it's working, sanity testing)\r\nD. Upgrade (suggest tweaking for now via DOC tix - overhaul that later)\r\nE. Other / Reference / Appendix (includes leftover and spurious existing sections)\r\n\r\nA. Install Eucalyptus\r\nADD: *high-level process* (mini-TOC of the following sections) HERE\r\n\r\n1. Plan your deployment - include layouts, describe the +services+ (let's stop calling them \"components\")\r\n a. POC layout\r\n b. one cluster\r\n c. multi-cluster\r\n d. describe choices (e.g., machine where the console could be installed, number of clusters, Walrus or Riak)\r\n e. mention pros/cons\r\n\r\n2. Install the CLC\r\nADD: prereq\r\ninitialize CLC - db, keys, eucaconf\r\n(clcadmin -init -cloud in 4.2 / 4.3)\r\n a. install\r\n b. initialize\r\n c. start\r\n d. verify CLC w/ euca-describe-services\r\n\r\n3. a. Register components (NOT the NCs)\r\nADD: prereq\r\n(another eucaconf command)\r\n(existing section good as is)\r\n(add prereq and verify)\r\n b. configure stuff like DNS (imaging service? security? load balancers?)\r\n\r\n4. Install the UFS\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install\r\n b. start\r\n c. verify UFS w/ euca-describe-services\r\n\r\n5. Install the Management Console (we said User Console but that's the old name)\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install (on the UFS, or point to the UFS)\r\n b. start\r\n c. create user\r\n d. verify by using the console with the user\r\n\r\n6. Install the NCs (n # of them, so loop)\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install\r\n b. configure bridge\r\n c. start\r\n(loop to install the next NC)\r\n\r\n7. Install the CC \r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install\r\n b. start\r\n c. register the nodes\r\n d. verify nodes are registered and enabled by going to the CLC euca-describe nodes (CLC goes through the CC to get to the NCs)\r\n\r\n8. Install the SC\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install\r\n b. start\r\n c. verify (it'll be in a broken state (as it says in the current doc))\r\n\r\n9. Install the OSG backend (Walrus or Riak)\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. install\r\n b. start\r\n c. verify (broken state here, too)\r\n\r\n=== Keri will do this storage related work via DOC-1562, DOC-1563 ===\r\n\r\n10. Configure storage (on CLC) - [~viglesias] my recollection of this section is less clear - tweak as needed please!\r\nADD: prereq\r\n a. Object storage (OSG) on Walrus or Riak\r\n(existing doc is good)\r\n(add prereq and verify)\r\n b. Block storage (on SC)\r\n(needs rewrite)\r\n(add prereq and verify)\r\n\r\n=== end storage related work by Keri ===\r\n\r\nB. Configure Network - Scott's to do in 4.2\r\n(network modes)\r\n(DNS here?)\r\n(add prereqs to each section, verify to each section)\r\n\r\nC. Verify Installation\r\nPrereqs:\r\n a. installed per above\r\n b. network in place\r\n c. at least one user login\r\n\r\n1. Install image emi-euca.com faststart (verifies OSG)\r\n2. run image and ping / SSH (verifies NC, instances, network)\r\n3. create volume\r\n4. attach to instance\r\n\r\nD. Upgrade\r\n(this release, use DOC tickets to tweak - we can revisit later - get \"fail first\" install done now)\r\n\r\nE. Other / Reference / Appendix\r\nFind More Info\r\nEuca Install from Local Package Repo\r\nEuca2ools Standalone Install\r\n(move Create Scheduling Policy here)\r\n(move Configure Loop Devices here)\r\n(move Configure Multi-Cluster Networking here)\r\n(kill HA in existing form === Keri to remove HA via DOC-1592 === )\r\n\r\nQuestions:\r\n(where does imaging service go?)\r\n{where does security groups' set up go?)\r\n(where do load balancers get configured?)","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=kmeredith","name":"kmeredith","key":"kmeredith","accountId":"557058:ad01e29f-e62e-4f95-b458-a96ea25c65e5","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8962f6c2075b2cf80ed6daccff85c8a7?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10100%26